Subset of libmicrohttpd sources http://www.gnu.org/software/libmicrohttpd/.

The libmicrohttpd is licensed under LGPL. The libmicrohttpd license and the
authors are in COPYING and AUTHORS files.

We have performed the following changes to the libmicrohttpd:
- code was converted to C++
- the ufal::microrestd::libmicrohttpd namespace was added
- we use compile-time configuration (see MHD_config.h) instead
  of configure script
